and make me sweet 16 again?

01:34:39.799 --> 01:34:41.466
It has nothing to do with me.

01:34:41.550 --> 01:34:44.844
Oh, you're a fine lad.
Your hand's in this, all right.

01:34:58.526 --> 01:35:01.611
